Title: Majik Blonde Hair Building Fiber(7 grams) With Optimizer Comb(Set of)
Description: Hair loss is a very common problem that number of people suffer from. There are number of products available in the market to prevent this problem. If you are suffering from a drastic hair fall and partial baldness, you could opt for Hair Building Fiber by Majik. Majik is a Swiss based brand which is recognized as one of the most reputed hair-care brands all over the world. From the Manufacturer What It Is Majik Hair Building Fibers, made of 100% Human hair, blend undetectably with existing hair strands to instantly create the appearance of naturally thick and full hair. What It Does Instantly fills in thinning areas Conceals hair loss Makes fine hair look completely thick and full Great as a root touch-up between colorings What Else You Need To Know Majik Hair Fibers resist wind, rain, and perspiration for long lasting results in all conditions. Available in nine shades that can be mixed to match Indian hair color, Hair Fibers work for all hair types and textures. Also great for part lines, covering extension tracks and touching up roots between hair color appointments. Easily washes out with shampoo. How to Apply Dry and style hair as usual. Shake Hair Fibers into thinning areas. If applying Hair Fibers near the hairline, use Majik Hairline Optimizer to achieve a natural looking front hairline. Gently pat hair to disperse Hair Fibers. If desired, lightly comb, brush, or style your hair after applying Hair Fibers. For best results, use Majik Hair Fiber Spray to finish for longer-lasting results.

Title: Rejsol TCA Peel 15% 30 ml(30 ml)
Description: Trichloroacetic Acid, TCA is Deep peeling agent, removes the superficial layer of skin thus promotes growth of new healthy skin Chemical Peels are acids therefore should be used under the Supervision of trained cosmetologists.Always do Patch Test when using the peel for the first time.Patch test: Apply small amount of peel below neck or armpit, see for any redness beyond the margin of application, if seendiscontinue the procedure. If no redness or itching continue with the procedureProcedure:Cleanse the skin with oil free cleanser, if using oil containing cleanser, after cleansing whip with alcohol or spirit. oil blocks the acid therefore desired action is not achieved.Apply Peel with brush or ear Buds, gel peels can be best applied with gloved fingers. start applying from the forehead upto the neck, application time should not be more than 20 seconds. keep peel for 3-7 mins depending on your skin habituality of peeling and the peel strength. Spray neutralizer, keep for 1 min.wash with water., apply sunscreen and good moisturiser for 7 days twice daily.Post Peel:Success of the peeling depends on sunprotection and moisturisingfirst the skin dies so becomes black don't worry this is the skin that is going to peel of itselfThere are two types of peeling microscopic that is not seen by naked eyes, and macroscopic peeling that is visualised very wellDo not remove the skin by your self.Don't use soap for 2-3 days, thereafter, use mild soap for 7-8 days, don't scrub too hardNote: If you don't get desired results doesnt mean the peel is not working it only means that your skin is tough for the peel you are using. then its time to use stronger peels or increase the application time of the peel in the next sitting.
